Cell.Data: Sent by the plugin automatically when DNA logs in successfully.
Sent when the user starts a game round by clicking on play button in menu. It's also sent when the application is resumed only if the session had been started.

Sent when the application is closed. It's also sent when the application is paused (it's sent to background). Some devices won't be able to send it when paused. Those devices will send it when resumed. It should be sent even though cutom.mobile.start hasn't been sent.
Sent when the user completes an in-app purchase implying real money.
Sent when the user spend currencies
Sent when the user clicks on the button to send a customer support ticket.
Sent when an ad is requested to show it to the user to pay for something.
Sent after the user has finished watching the ad or when the ad is aborted.
Sent when the user starts a run (after clicking on menu play button).
Send when dragon die while game run
Send when player finished run (exact moment doesn't matter)
When player gain HC, SC or pieces of golden egg
